title: Anal Angel
description: The members of the fish paste club include Arisugawa Sakura, the school's number one trap, Aoi sensei, their club advisor and a beautiful trap himself, and Kurumi, their youngest member. Thanks to Sakura's appeal, Kurumi gets pulled into the strange, sexual world of the fish paste club, but will he be able to win Sakura's heart away from his childhood friend?
